    .process.full
      .description
        p A marketplace for Artists and Art buyers. Want Art At has an innovating concept in how to bid or select the right price to sell your art pieces. Want Art At had already a prove of concept created, however the design they had was amateurish and was not working to get the feedback they needed from their users in order to execute the idea.
