      h1 Design of ui and ux
      p Want Art At's target is artists and art lovers so whilst the app had to have a clean interface it also needed to speak to the artist's mind.
      p We worked on all views of this app in Invision where our design team collaborated with Want Art At's team so that we could arrive to a product.
